ZMQ Bounce - A Utility for bouncing messages with ZMQ


zbserver listens on tcp://localhost:5655, sending a message on
epgm://;224.0.0.1:5656 every time it revieves one.

zbclient sends messages on tcp://localhost:5655, waiting for a message
on epgm://;224.0.0.1:5656 every time it has sent one.

To compile, just run `make all`.
